"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft5x1DAD.jpg&h=84e6c9e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢中學嗰陣時已經識得成日搵着數 之前仲有幫元氣壽司賣廣告 <br />\n可能佢覺得自己讀ece懷才不遇所以轉行做老千<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5BwmDCn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5BwmDCn.png&h=a43a2b2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n究竟真係uber eat搵佢定係佢自己叫外賣然後扮KOL呢？十分好奇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wX0fcEo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwX0fcEo.jpg&h=82c36812&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SwFiUSK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSwFiUSK.jpg&h=5d8174eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dtyTJL5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdtyTJL5.jpg&h=b7158d58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kUOz7CM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkUOz7CM.png&h=7eb1df29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講到幾咁想幫人 要幫人發達<br />\n實際係要人借錢借到盡 升做41 咁佢就可以湊夠6個41 升做42<br />\n睇黎佢幫人負債係有一手<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ODv6Ymi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FODv6Ymi.jpg&h=1386d948&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n伯母洗緊既1萬蚊 洗完會折福<br />\n污糟錢黎 成手血呀伯母<br />\n<br />\n第5位老千: 鵬燕玲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GONMYmJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGONMYmJ.jpg&h=7fc98825&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AS5bp1K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAS5bp1K.jpg&h=028e18bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RjgaHU9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRjgaHU9.png&h=3850c8ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n身為幼稚園老師 呃左人40萬 幾時還返D錢比人呀?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pfhUrsH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpfhUrsH.png&h=8a07127d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hrBh8F3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhrBh8F3.png&h=a6ae56db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢堆老千為左錢不擇手段 連有精神病患既人都搞<br />\n為左錢 令到人冇左份工 再借左財仔40萬 人地點哂你名呀<br />\n許巧莉 湛灝霖 關嘉儀 黃錦恩<br />\n你地點樣補償返呢位苦主? 人地就黎要跳樓"}]}